  abstract  = "OBJECTIVE: The American College of Surgeons Committee on Trauma
               has created a ``Trauma Quality Improvement Program'' (TQIP) that
               uses the existing infrastructure of Committee on Trauma
               programs. As the first step toward full implementation of TQIP,
               a pilot study was conducted in 23 American College of Surgeons
