               blunt multisystem, 2: penetrating truncal, and 3: blunt
               single-system injury). Benchmark reports were developed with
               each center's risk adjusted mortality (expressed as an
               observed-to-expected [O/E] mortality ratio and 90\% confidence
               interval [CI]) and crude complication rates available for
